    "title": {
      "rendered": "9 Fundraising Tools to Watch in 2015"
    },
    "content": {
      "rendered": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/9-Fundraising-Tools-to-Watch-in-2015.jpg\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-17646\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/9-Fundraising-Tools-to-Watch-in-2015-300x300.jpg?resize=300%2C300\" alt=\"9 Fundraising Tools to Watch in 2015\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/9-Fundraising-Tools-to-Watch-in-2015.jpg?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/9-Fundraising-Tools-to-Watch-in-2015.jpg?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/9-Fundraising-Tools-to-Watch-in-2015.jpg?resize=200%2C200&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/9-Fundraising-Tools-to-Watch-in-2015.jpg?resize=75%2C75&amp;ssl=1 75w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/9-Fundraising-Tools-to-Watch-in-2015.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a>Over the last six months Nonprofit Tech for Good has bookmarked over 50 fundraising tools to prepare for this blog post. When the time came to write the post, at least 25% of the fundraising tools had shut down. It is very difficult to launch a fundraising service that is sustainable i.e., can earn enough revenue to pay staff, keep the lights on,\u00a0and continually invest in innovation. \u00a0That said, the nine fundraising tools listed below are good ideas whose time has time come. Most are still a work in progress, but they stand out in 2015 as services that might be around for awhile.</p>\n<hr />\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">1.\u00a0<a href=\"http://snapdonate.org/\" target=\"_blank\">SnapDonate</a></h2>\n<p>A mobile app that enables users to donate by simply pointing their phone at a charity logo. The app will automatically recognize the logo and then users select the amount to donate.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://snapdonate.org/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17616\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/SnapDonate.png?resize=600%2C288\" alt=\"SnapDonate\" width=\"600\" height=\"288\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/SnapDonate.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/SnapDonate.png?resize=300%2C144&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">2.\u00a0<a href=\"http://promiseorpay.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Promise or Pay</a></h2>\n<p>A service that enables users to make a promise (to exercise at least 5 times a week, for example) or pay/donate to participating nonprofits.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://promiseorpay.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17641\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Promise-or-Pay.png?resize=600%2C286\" alt=\"Promise or Pay\" width=\"600\" height=\"286\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Promise-or-Pay.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Promise-or-Pay.png?resize=300%2C143&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">3.\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.ongood.ngo/portal/\" target=\"_blank\">OnGood</a></h2>\n<p>A multilingual, mobile responsive global directory of validiated NGOs that will enable users to donate to NGOs worldwide in 80+ currencies (coming May 2015). The validation process is completed through the purchase of the <strong><a href=\"https://www.ongood.ngo/whois\" target=\"_blank\">.NGO and .ONG domains</a></strong>.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.ongood.ngo/portal/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17624\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/ongood.png?resize=600%2C263\" alt=\"ongood\" width=\"600\" height=\"263\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/ongood.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/ongood.png?resize=300%2C131&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">4.\u00a0<a href=\"http://www.kidsgive.com.au/\" target=\"_blank\">Kids Give</a></h2>\n<p>With a focus on the emerging online power of\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/nonprofitorgs/status/577089835183136768\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>#Philanthrokids</strong></a>, this is a crowdfunding service build specifically for Gen Z kids who want fundraise for causes that they care about.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kidsgive.com.au/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17632\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Kids-Give.png?resize=600%2C286\" alt=\"Kids Give\" width=\"600\" height=\"286\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Kids-Give.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Kids-Give.png?resize=300%2C143&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">5.\u00a0<a href=\"https://goodworld.me/\" target=\"_blank\">Good World</a></h2>\n<p>Tapping into the power of hashtags on Facebook and Twitter, this service enables users to donate by simply using the hashtag #Donate in their status updates and tweets.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://goodworld.me/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17638\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Good-World.png?resize=600%2C281\" alt=\"Good World\" width=\"600\" height=\"281\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Good-World.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Good-World.png?resize=300%2C140&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">6.\u00a0<a href=\"http://www.giveapp.org/\" target=\"_blank\">Give App</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">\u00a0A mobile app that enables two-tap donations to any nonprofit in the United States, <strong><a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/2014/07/27/new-mobile-app-will-change-the-way-donors-give-and-nonprofits-fundraise/\">Nonprofit Tech for Good has written about this app before</a></strong>.\u00a0A VC firm or entreprenuer should fund this app fast and help bring it to the next level!</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.giveapp.org/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17627\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Give-App.png?resize=600%2C332\" alt=\"Give App\" width=\"600\" height=\"332\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Give-App.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Give-App.png?resize=300%2C166&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">7.\u00a0<a href=\"https://dollaraday.co/\" target=\"_blank\">Dollar A Day</a></h2>\n<p>A service that enables donors to sign up to automatically donate $30 a month where $1 is donated each day to a different nonprofit. Users are sent a daily email featuring the nonprofit.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://dollaraday.co/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17630\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Dollar-A-Day.png?resize=600%2C276\" alt=\"Dollar A Day\" width=\"600\" height=\"276\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Dollar-A-Day.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Dollar-A-Day.png?resize=300%2C138&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">8.\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.charitweet.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Charitweet</a></h2>\n<p>A service that enables Twitterers to donate by sending tweets. All that is required is that Twitterers\u00a0send tweets (or retweets) that include &#8220;@Charitweet&#8221; and &#8220;@CharityName&#8221; as well as the &#8220;$(Amount). &#8221;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.charitweet.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17621\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/charitweet.png?resize=600%2C286\" alt=\"charitweet\" width=\"600\" height=\"286\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/charitweet.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/charitweet.png?resize=300%2C143&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">9.\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.atpay.com/\" target=\"_blank\">@Pay</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">A service that\u00a0enables users to donate in two taps by either replying to an email or a text message. Get ready! The days of donors entering their name, address, and credit card information into online forms are coming to an end.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.atpay.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17635\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/atpay.png?resize=600%2C318\" alt=\"atpay\" width=\"600\" height=\"318\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/atpay.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/atpay.png?resize=300%2C159&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<hr />\n<table style=\"border-color: transparent; width: 600px; background-color: #ffffff;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" align=\"center\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/social-and-mobile-media-webinars-for-nonprofits/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-17655\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/TWO.png?resize=299%2C167\" alt=\"TWO\" width=\"299\" height=\"167\" /></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/social-and-mobile-media-training-for-nonprofits/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-17656\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/ONE.png?resize=299%2C167\" alt=\"ONE\" width=\"299\" height=\"167\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n",
